sequenceDiagram
  participant UI as GUI
  participant API as gui-server
  participant Sync as syncCoursePublicAssets
  participant Batch as renderAllModules
  participant Rem as remotion CLI
  UI->>API: POST /api/render-course
  API->>Sync: copy assets + timings
  API->>Batch: spawn tsx process
  loop each module
    Batch->>Rem: npx remotion render
    Rem-->>API: stdout Rendered X/Y
    API-->>UI: SSE progress events
  end
  Batch-->>API: exit code
  API-->>UI: SSE done
